    How do I wash the Bedsheet?

    Caring for Your LiveGrounded Earthing Sheets

     

    The silver threads in your grounding sheets naturally have antibacterial properties, but regular washing is essential to remove sweat and oils that can obstruct conductivity.

    To ensure consistent grounding and maximum benefits, we recommend rotating between multiple sheets, so you never have to miss a night of deep, restorative sleep.

    Washing Instructions:

    ✔ Use warm water to effectively remove sweat and body oils.
    ✔ Machine wash at least twice a month, or more frequently if needed.
    ✔ Opt for mild liquid detergents such as Tide Gentle or Seventh Generation for best results.

     

    Drying:

    ✔ Line dry whenever possible for longevity.
    ✔ If using a dryer, tumble dry on low heat.

    Ironing:

    ✔ Safe to iron on low heat when necessary.

     

    Avoid:

    ✖ Bleach, whitening agents, oxi-detergents, and fabric softeners (these can damage conductivity).
    ✖ Detergents with essential oils (Eucalyptus, Lavender, or citrus oils can coat silver threads).
    ✖ Applying lotions or body oils within an hour before bed (this can interfere with conductivity).

     

    For optimal performance and longevity, line drying is always preferred over tumble drying. Taking care of your grounding sheets means longer-lasting, uninterrupted nights of healing sleep. 🌎💤

    What is Grounding?

    "Earthing" or "Grounding" – The Science-Backed Secret to Recharging Your Body

    Biohackers like Bryan Johnson, holistic doctors, and top wellness experts all recognize the profound effects of Earthing—a practice as natural as it is powerful.

    Earthing is the act of physically reconnecting with the Earth's natural energy, often by walking barefoot on grass or soil, or using highly conductive grounding sheets to bring these benefits indoors.

    By tapping into the Earth's natural negative charge, we allow our bodies—which are naturally bioelectrical—to rebalance, reduce inflammation, and restore energy levels.

    But modern lifestyles keep us insulated from this healing ground force, cutting off a key source of natural regulation. Think of it like recharging your body's battery, the way plugging in your phone restores its power.

    Leading wellness pioneers are already embracing this science-backed practice for better sleep, lower stress, and deeper recovery. Read on to discover the life-changing benefits of Earthing...

    Revolutionizing Grounding – 8 Hours of Healing While You Sleep

    The LiveGrounded Earthing Sheet brings the science of grounding indoors, allowing you to connect with the Earth’s natural energy for a full 8 hours—without stepping outside.

    By linking directly to your home’s grounding system, these innovative sheets transfer the Earth’s free electrons into your body while you sleep, replicating the effects of walking barefoot on the ground.

    This uninterrupted connection neutralizes the harmful effects of dirty electricity, bringing your body back to its natural electrical state. As you sleep, your body's deepest healing and regenerative processes are activated, promoting restorative sleep, reduced inflammation, and cellular repair.

    Now, instead of grounding for just a few minutes outdoors, you can restore your body all night long—effortlessly. 🌿⚡💤
